Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing dramatic is guaranteed to happen\Njust because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's not going to be\Na great memory or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how grand is this phenomenon\Nknown as Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a right way to celebrate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this luck that supposedly\Ncomes with Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does something that's born\Non Christmas shine bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:42.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Good Luck"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly are you\Nsupposed to do on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. U-Um, Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:01:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take Christmas...\NMay I take the 25th off?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...call it that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, is a date where you do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,something fun with someone you're\Ninterested in to get closer to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that case, I guess you could\Nsort of call this a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My date with Shimamura...\NWhat should we do on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken, a cake, a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A present for Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A present, a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A Christmas present for Shimamura--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, Adachicchi! What're you spaced out for?\NYou feeling faint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be waiting for Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's rare to see you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. She's not here.\NHow did she lose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need to wait for Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't usually get the chance\Nto ask you out to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the grub!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what Shimamura likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she have anything she actually likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the type of person that\Nactually talks about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been shopping with Shimamura before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, but it's usually like a bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we've peeked in a tea shop before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we went because of me,\Nbut Shimamura did have a look, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I think there was a certain tea\Nthat she said smelled good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember if it\Nwas black tea or green...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't happen to remember\Nthe name of that tea, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what was it? It wasn't barley tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Which shelf was it on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is on the tip of my tongue, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can remember it if I see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see it... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you look for it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I mean, you could just\Ntake Shimamura with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go with you and choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.\NWhere'd you get lost at, Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you shrink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just you seem smaller than usual,\Nso I lost track of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I have some ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over some bread, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,There's a sweet one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,Ooh, give me that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'd ever... be able to smack\NShimamura on the head like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Adatty, have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She apparently had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a day like that like\Nonce a year. Anyway, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Do you want to get on the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, but we should\Nget away from school first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If a teacher sees us,\Nwe'll never hear the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought of you as an honor student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Praise me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it is pretty weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm imagining walking around town\Non Christmas with another girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and my heart is about to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Shimamura isn't\Nthis anxious about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely a difference in how\NI feel about Shimamura and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure if I want her\Nto realize that... or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:22.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Jikkokuya Jyugoro"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Ginger Tea"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I may or may not have someone\Nin my family who drinks a lot of tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginger... That'd probably warm you right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it works great\Nfor people who get cold easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my family member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't exactly get cold easily.\NLet's see, where was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it was on this shelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adatty. Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the type that would get mad\Nif I confidently told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yeah, this is the one!" and was totally wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think my personality sucks that badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. Then I think it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man... Thanks for treating me.\NThough I sorta talked you into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit chilly in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally anxious because you\Ndon't know what to say right now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it would've been the same\Nwith Nagafuji here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, in her case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what she had to do...\NDid you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief. What am I going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not. They seem busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Adatty, always the honor student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...that got to hang out\Nwith Shimamura alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Why were you with Nagafuji?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that I was totally wrong\Nabout that shouldn't hurt this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the sound of her name was enough\Nto get me through this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really an alien, Yachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, tsk, tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course. I have never told a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then show me proof!\NProof that you're an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk, tsk, tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be violating my agreement\Nif I showed you, so I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules of the universe\Ncan be rather strict. Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that, Little Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, my, what a dramatic sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that's dramatic, Yachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just breathe into it more gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's almost discount time, so I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alienspeak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura and I are just normal friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's how Shimamura sees us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I still want to get\Ncloser to Shimamura one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:30.02,OS,,0,0,0,,"Where do you want to meet?"\N"Does 1 PM at the usual mall work?"\N"Roger"\N"I'm looking forward to tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But the closer you get,\Nthe more things get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep mentioning Christmas\Nwith Shimamura, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it love? No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Romance? No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, it's warm and fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a warm liquid that flows through my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this "Cool" supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "Coolio"? Maybe she meant, "Chill out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, "Cool beans"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear Shimamura's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be able to hear\Nand ask her lots tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you sitting here\Nfor the last five minutes from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I was just joking. Anyway,\Nsorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've been wondering\Never since I saw you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing your Chinese dress\Nfrom work under your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... Yeah, I guess I can't\Nblame you for wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,won't people think you're trying\Nto lure them into a sketchy shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, even I know this is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But... She said I looked cute in it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think it's fine. You look super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice being so pretty.\NYou can actually pull that outfit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But you're even cuter Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can skip the sarcasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas all alone with Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,So, where are you taking me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Shimamura's probably only here\Nbecause she felt obligated as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,Um, we should go to the 2nd floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stop. Whenever I let my guard down,\Nmy thoughts just go down a dark path
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll get depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suddenly grab my hand\Nlike a purse-snatcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we do this all before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, make sure you just ask if it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of response is that?\NHow did you even pronounce that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've sounded like a shrimp just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore that. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, though. I'll ask next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to panic so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else is going to steal my hand from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the only one\Nthat gets to walk next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking we could play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... An arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. A ping-pong table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We could play... this. Air hockey.\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Air hockey is sort of similar\Nto ping-pong in some ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This was our pastime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,You can go first, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,Okay, take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura and I met\Non the second floor of the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how it happened, once we've met,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a path that\Nled us there as well as fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the encounter, there's always\Na grand past that goes along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,This is sorta different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:47.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,I play the video game version\Nof this at home with my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hundred, 500, billions of\Nactions done by everyone and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,and it's definitely a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,piled up together in order\Nfor two people to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of paths led us to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one different decision would've meant\Nthat I wouldn't have met Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that fact alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Made me endlessly like my past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're pretty good at this, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How you like them apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Adachi. You're super good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected you to be\Nthe type to pick on noobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you also had more wins\Nin ping-pong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair to make stuff up\Njust because I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't seem that long ago somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When spring comes and we become second-years\Nand the sun is out more again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we're gonna go to the gym again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can just go to class,\Ncome here after school, and play ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect score. You're a total\Nhonor student now, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, we're gonna be second-years...\NWe'll probably be in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you a Christmas gift... or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Well, this was a nice surprise.\NCan I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. This is the nice smelling one.\NI wanted to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you know I liked this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Oh, you must've asked Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't have to, Adachi.\NBut thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be\Nthinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're such a good little girl, Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis got you a present, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A boomerang... Oh, and some goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to wear it\Nwhen I throw this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Oh, I threw it\Na few times before buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way more fun than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck at choosing stuff like this,\Nso I asked Nagafuji to help me pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she'd want a boomerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think kids would love them. They're super fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they tend to snap when you\Nthrow them around in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:20:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just told Nagafuji I was getting\Na present for my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji... I see.\NSo that's why she was with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks... I'll take really good care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I didn't care\Nabout the boomerang, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Shimamura gave this to me...\Nwas the best gift I could ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah. You hold the boomerang behind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and then throw it in front of you like you're\Ngoing to chop something vertically.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that. Make sure you\Ndon't throw it up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's your first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to catch it, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But that's not bad for a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sorta look like you're in some movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing that thing in your Chinese dress.\NIt's very cinematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not feeling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Hey, should I go back\Nand buy you something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But we probably should head back.\NIt's warmer inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This was my only chance, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, where no one else was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:22:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only place I'd be able to say\Nsomething like this to Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not ready...\NEven if I fall on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, really like you... love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to be your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure we already are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not just friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be like, your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:23:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sorta really want to be that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's great that you're so ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing dramatic is guaranteed to happen\Njust because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's not going to be\Na great memory or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, my mind just kept going blank,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so I didn't really have a chance\Nto remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like scenery being covered in snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to carve the memory of\Na white album into the back of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:52.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 6: 'White Album'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:24:07.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time:\N'Please Choose the Best Chocolate for Me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.31,0:23:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mad about, Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:23:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some chicken curry\Nat my place on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas, so chicken curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's a Nagafuji family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Guess I'll just have to come over then!
